            "correct_answer": "ក=kaa, គ=kea | ក=kah, គ=keah | ក=kam, គ=koam",
            "explanation": "Sun (ក) keeps vowels clean: kaa, kah, kam\nMoon (គ) shifts them with E/O: kea, keah, koam\nThis is the COMMANDER PRINCIPLE."
